long_description: You are standing in front of the Slums- I mean the Manors.
short_description: You look out at the road out front of the Manors.

long_description: You are standing inside the dining hall. The smell of rotten food floods your nostrils.
You are standing in the tennis courts which are in ruins.
You are standing by a fountain that never runs. Like never. Like you would've thought that for all the money they spent on it, it would run, but it doesn't. Ain't that something?
You are inside the deserted Business Building.
short_description: You glance around the once full classrooms.

long_description: You quietly stand in the lobby of the Library. To your left are some doors leading downstairs.
short_description: You glance around the full desks trying not to make a sound.

long_description: You are inspired by previous success when seeing the Spartain Rock between Johnson and Humanities.
You stand on a brick path between Humanities and the Library.
short_description: You glance around and see a fountain in the distance.

long_description: You are standing outside of Northside Commons.
short_description: You glance around the lawn of Northside Commons.
